name: The CATYCLOPS Revealed
description: The latest telemetry reports have come in from the galactic front lines, and the CATYCLOPS is definitely on the move. In search of it's beloved Planets with Rings. Is our own Saturn in peril? More data is coming in daily. We were able to decode one last transmitted 4-dimensional schematic scan from our spy star vessel before it was, sadly, devoured. Created via VR, 3D, and internet magic.
